text: Margit Kövessi (1 September 1907 - 30 August 1992) was a Hungarian gymnast. She competed in the women's artistic team all-around event at the 1928 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1907 births Category:1992 deaths Category:Hungarian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Hungary Category:Gymnasts at the 1928 Summer Olympics Category:People from Banská Štiavnica
